<tree text="Puttaka&#x1E47;&#x1E0D;a" target="text">
  <text>
    <hangnum nr="281"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Abhijātaṃ  anujātaṃ, puttamicchanti paṇḍitā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Avajātaṃ na icchanti, yo hoti kulagandhano.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="282"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Pañcaṭṭhānāni  sampassaṃ, puttamicchanti paṇḍitā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Bhato vā no bharissati, kiccaṃ vā no karissati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="283"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kulavaṃso ciraṃ tiṭṭhe, dāyajjaṃ paṭipajjati;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Atha vā pana petānaṃ, dakkhinaṃ anupadassati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="284"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Bahuputte  pitā eko, avassaṃ poseti sadā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Bahuputtā na sakkonti, posetuṃ pitarekakaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="285"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Puttaṃ vā bhātaraṃ duṭṭhu, anusāseyya no jahe;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Kinnu chejjaṃ karaṃ pādaṃ, littaṃ asucinā siyā.</gatha>
  </text>
